summary: Don't snatch the wings off butterflies. Just catch them in jars.
descriptionHtml:
Don't snatch the wings off butterflies. Just catch them in jars.

This only works for the 5 bugs in jars.
Bees
Torchbugs
Orange Dartwings
Monarch Butterflies
Luna Moths

I don't know how to add other things to the inside of jars, but if somebody else knows, please tell me. I want to save the blue butterflies too.

Also, they are still ingredients that you can still use in alchemy. They just aren't dead yet.
author: youbetterwork
